Each job folder such job1, job2 and job3, contain 3 sub-folders:
agent - this folder container the instruction file for the agent to complete the job.
inbox - this folder container the files to be processes.
outbox - this folder container the output and log for the job.

The agent has to read the instruction and complete the jobs found in this folder.


